Hi {USERNAME}, Your UPS system, {UPSNAME}, with model {MODEL} is currently {STATUS}. Its line voltage is currently {LINEV} and the battery charge is {BCHARGE}. Running with a load capacity of {LOADPCT}, you will have {TIMELEFT} on battery power.
